name: Run Kitty Run game for the iPhone / iPad (Canceled)
blurb: Run to the end of each level and dodge the dogs along the way. Play alone or together in this cute re-imagining of an old concept!

rewards.reward: Show your support and get access to backers-only updates + an open ear to listen to your suggestions & opinions for the game. I'd love to hear you out. It's the least I can do to show you my appreciation. Drop me an e-mail and I promise to find time to respond. Any ideas I use will be properly credited to you. You also already have voting rights for any decisions/designs that need community ideas

Wow....I don't think anyone will choose this, but if so, you get all of the above + (chances are...it will be far) I would surely want to personally fly to meet you so that I'm able to shake your hand, treat you to some good food, and hand you all the above gifts in person + I'd even give you a complete copy of the documented code for Run Kitty Run (but like the art, you can't re-distribute it, or use it commercially in the sense that you just change some things and re-sell the game, but I don't mind if you use my code for reference for parts of your own project).
